{"tid":2165734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府派樽日日剩 收回率不足68%  全民檢測料僅一成人參與","createTime":"2020-08-20T04:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T04:35:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b638b97b25ac71d2a627348907a44b9477304c6","tid":2165734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/AAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FAAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRuff3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=de0c036c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FAAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI%2F&h=365bd58e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/AAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n政府派樽日日剩 收回率不足68% <br />\n全民檢測料僅一成人參與<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港第三波武肺疫情近日明顯放緩，林鄭政府才強推全民病毒檢測，更揚言會有500萬人參與。本報分析醫管局普通科門診派樽計劃數據，發現自7月27日計劃開展至8月15日，派發率只有85.4%，收回率更只有約67.7%，有門診一日僅得30多名市民索取樣本包，場面冷清，反映公眾參與檢測意欲低。有專家直指，只有自覺有感染風險及有病徵者，才有動機參與檢測，料全民檢測最多只有50萬人參與，僅及政府估算的一成。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：專家︰集中檢測群組才能撲火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lLVZR0M6PJdAAn0M1T2ZDj-FF7M=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GLEDTDJYCVBTTABRUCOWPTXSGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlLVZR0M6PJdAAn0M1T2ZDj-FF7M%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGLEDTDJYCVBTTABRUCOWPTXSGI.jpg&h=78e01f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中九龍診所平均每日只派出約30份樣本包，只及總量110份的三成多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oFJFSDtlD39C_ZS5tmnkFqfZtSk=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R2TY47QMA5HYHF73XUNFMUGVRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoFJFSDtlD39C_ZS5tmnkFqfZtSk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR2TY47QMA5HYHF73XUNFMUGVRM.jpg&h=cd2020f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何栢良指若想短時間內中斷社區傳播鏈，須於兩三日內為高危群組完成檢測。<br />\n<br />\n各項武肺檢測計劃中，醫管局轄下22間普通科門診自7月27日起，每日每間向公眾派發110個樣本樽，性質最接近全民檢測。醫管局表示，截至8月15日，已派發逾3.1萬份樣本包及完成約2.1萬份檢測，找到50份陽性樣本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中九龍診所每日僅派出三成<br />\n<br />\n本報計算後發現，若醫管局每日派盡樣本包，7月27日至8月15日實應派出3.63萬份，換言之，派發率只有85.4%。據了解，收集的。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：火眼實驗室欠認證 無罰則監管<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aerty0rxSqaXvLG6YTU5TlH1jsk=/1715x1064/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IL33OONZI5DH5HEK75G2IXRKCE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Faerty0rxSqaXvLG6YTU5TlH1jsk%3D%2F1715x1064%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIL33OONZI5DH5HEK75G2IXRKCE.gif&h=20be0182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本報記者本周二早上於中九龍診所觀察診所派樽一小時，僅約30名市民索取樣本包，只及總量110份的三成多，並不踴躍。。。。。。<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超指出，只有兩類人有動機參加全民檢測，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n梁又指，收集深喉唾液樣本是最方便，同樣可做混合檢測，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何栢良︰太遲找出確診個案<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良亦指出，本港疫情最大問題是太遲找出確診個案再隔離病人。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a3d1f110db07e53c0d08416ed2399ced6fd67802","tid":2165734,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"紅色衫阿叔講緊咩野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf3a6c63f06b56f2bb51c078058c5d2506b860c","tid":2165734,"uid":30274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"僅1成白痴會自動獻上DNA<br />\n<br />\n所以下一步就係強制檢測<br />\n冇監控送中碼就唔比入餐廳，去店舖購物，乘搭公共交通，出入公共場所，出入境香港<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講直接將支那套信用評級搬黎香港用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac